edu.xtec.jclic.bags

Class MediaBag

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.jclic.bags.MediaBag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Editable, Domable, StreamIO.InputStreamProvider

    public class MediaBag
extends Object
implements Editable, Domable, StreamIO.InputStreamProvider
    This class stores and manages all the media components (images, sounds, animations, video, MIDI files, etc.) needed to run the activities of a JClicProject. The main member of the class is a ArrayList that stores MediaBagElement objects. It defines also a MediaBag.Listener interface to allow other objects to be informed about changes in the media collection.
    Version:
    13.09.10
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
